# Convert

Convert static safetensor embedding models to binary format for the C++ server.

## Install Dependencies

```bash
cd train
uv pip install huggingface-hub safetensors tokenizers
```

## Usage

```bash
cd train
source .venv/bin/activate
python ../convert/convert.py minishlab/potion-base-2M
```

This will:
1. Download the model from HuggingFace Hub
2. Extract the embeddings tensor
3. Convert to delta-encoded binary format
4. Save as `minishlab_potion-base-2M.bin`

### Specify output path

```bash
python convert.py minishlab/potion-base-2M -o my_embeddings.bin
```

### Use with a private model

```bash
python convert.py <private_model> --token hf_xxxxx
```

### List available tensors

```bash
python convert.py minishlab/potion-base-2M --list
```

## Run the server

```bash
./build/dist/embedder minishlab_potion-base-2M.bin
```
